#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.umbrello.appdata.xml:9
msgid "Umbrello"
msgstr "Umbrello"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.umbrello.appdata.xml:10
msgid "UML Modeller"
msgstr "UML modelatzailea"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.umbrello.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"Umbrello is a Unified Modelling Language (UML) modelling tool and code "
"generator. It can create diagrams of software and other systems in the "
"industry-standard UML format, and can also generate code from UML diagrams "
"in a variety of programming languages."
msgstr ""
"Umbrello UML (Unified Modelling Language - modelatzeko lengoaia bateratua) "
"modelatzeko tresna bat eta kode-sortzaile bat da. Software-diagramak eta "
"beste sistema batzuk sor ditzake industriaren UML formatu estandarrean, eta "
"UML diagrametatik kodea sor dezake hainbat lengoaiatan."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.umbrello.appdata.xml:17
msgid "Features:"
msgstr "Ezaugarriak:"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.umbrello.appdata.xml:19
msgid "Supported formats: XMI"
msgstr "Onartutako formatuak: XMI"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.umbrello.appdata.xml:20
msgid ""
"Several type of diagrams supported: use case, class, sequence, "
"communication, state, activity, component, deployment, entity relationship"
msgstr ""
"Zenbait diagrama mota onartzen ditu: erabilera kasua, klasea, sekuentzia, "
"lankidetza, egoera, jarduera, osagaia, hedatzea, entitate-erlazioa"

#. (itstool) path: screenshot/caption
#: org.kde.umbrello.appdata.xml:30
msgid "Showing class diagram"
msgstr "Klase-diagrama erakusten"
